'''馬庫斯·威利斯'''（'''Marcus Willis'''，{{bd|1990年|10月9日}}）是已退役的[[英國|英國]]職業[[網球|網球]]選手。他在[[2016年溫布爾登網球錦標賽|2016年溫布爾登網球錦標賽]]上首次參加ATP巡迴賽。<ref name="Qualifying">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/tennis/36623880 |title=Wimbledon: Britain's world number 775 Marcus Willis qualifies for main draw |website=BBC Sport|date=24 June 2016}}</ref>

==早期生涯和個人生活==
威利斯自9歲就開始打網球了。他的母親是一位小學教師，父親則是一位會計師<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/players/marcus-willis/w521/bio |title=Marcus Willis |work=atpworldtour.com |publisher=Association of Tour Professionals |accessdate=29 June 2016 }}</ref>。威利斯曾就讀於聖保羅小學和{{link-en|文納什森林學校|The Forest School, Winnersh}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/tennis/2016/06/27/wimbledon-2016-who-is-marcus-willis/|title=Wimbledon 2016: Who is Marcus Willis, the new British hero at SW19? |newspaper=Telegraph|date=27 June 2016}}</ref>。威利斯現在和珍妮佛·貝特（Jennifer Bate）交往，她是一位[[國民保健署_(英國)|國民保健署]]牙醫和前選美冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-3665875/Marcus-Willis-s-girlfriend-arrives-cheer-player-against-Roger-Federer.html |title=
Brit underdog Marcus Willis begins his Centre Court battle with tennis royalty Roger Federer in front of the ex-beauty queen who saved his career |newspaper=Daily Mail|date=29 June 2016}}</ref>。威利斯現在在一所獨立女校擔任教師。

==少年生涯==
在2008年澳網開始之前，威利斯曾一度因無視對他懈怠態度的最後警告而被英國[[草地网球协会|草地网球协会]]送回家<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/tennis/a-new-hope-for-british-tennis-772706.html|title=A new hope for British tennis?|newspaper=Independent|date=23 January 2008}}</ref><ref name="Independent 27 July 16">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/tennis/wimbledon-roger-federer-next-for-british-sensation-marcus-willis-after-amazing-victory-a7106566.html|title=Wimbledon: Roger Federer next for British sensation Marcus Willis after amazing victory|newspaper=Independent|date=27 July 2016}}</ref>。在2008年9月，他的世界少年排名達到15位，是他的最高排名。

